    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been meticulously preserved, showing no signs of wear and offering a driving experience that is truly like new. If you're looking for the very best, this is the one for you!",
