    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant restoration or can be used for parts. The exterior shows substantial wear, including noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and likely needs a head gasket replacement, and the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. The interior has seen heavy use, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car for someone with the time and resources to invest in a complete overhaul.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the suspension is a bit noisy over bumps and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant rust and several large dents. The interior upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears. The engine requires major repairs and the transmission is slipping.",
      "price": 5500.0,
